1
00:01:24,080 --> 00:01:30,190
[Sunshine of My LIfe]

2
00:01:30,190 --> 00:01:32,870
[Episode 21]

3
00:01:36,470 --> 00:01:39,070
Dad, you're not sleeping yet?

4
00:01:41,550 --> 00:01:44,040
You're mature now. Even have a girlfriend in France.

5
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:46,740
Why haven't I heard you mention it?

6
00:01:47,370 --> 00:01:49,430
It wasn't confirmed before.

7
00:01:49,430 --> 00:01:51,660
- Is it confirmed now?
- Yes.

8
00:01:51,660 --> 00:01:55,260
Look at you. You've always been sensible.

9
00:01:55,260 --> 00:01:59,760
When it comes to you handling your personal things, I don't want to say much.

10
00:01:59,760 --> 00:02:02,770
I hope that you won't fight

11
00:02:02,770 --> 00:02:05,640
with your mom about this, okay?

12
00:02:06,720 --> 00:02:08,980
We can forget what happened in the past.

13
00:02:08,980 --> 00:02:10,690
But you must remember one thing.

14
00:02:10,690 --> 00:02:14,480
That woman in that room who gave birth and raised you is your mother.

15
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:17,490
You know when Mom is being domineering,

16
00:02:17,490 --> 00:02:18,940
who can deal with her?

17
00:02:18,940 --> 00:02:22,880
I promise you then. When she's being domineering, I'll defend you.

18
00:02:22,880 --> 00:02:25,490
- Remember what you said.
- Of course. Here.

19
00:02:27,790 --> 00:02:31,360
But you have to give her some time and let her adjust slowly.

20
00:02:31,360 --> 00:02:34,210
You know she's the person in this world who is most concerned about you.

21
00:02:34,210 --> 00:02:36,590
That you have to admit.

22
00:02:36,590 --> 00:02:38,120
I understand.

23
00:02:38,120 --> 00:02:40,640
So when dealing with women,

24
00:02:40,640 --> 00:02:44,480
you must have the right way. Right?

25
00:02:44,480 --> 00:02:47,730
You can't ruin relationships just because of this matter.

26
00:02:47,730 --> 00:02:49,740
- Do you know what I mean?
- Yes.

27
00:02:49,740 --> 00:02:52,960
I must learn more from you in terms of dealing with women.

28
00:02:54,240 --> 00:02:56,440
She's all worked up in the room.

29
00:02:56,440 --> 00:03:00,410
Get some of her favorite grapes and take them to her. Be good.

30
00:03:03,240 --> 00:03:05,460
You're such a great husband.

31
00:03:05,460 --> 00:03:07,400
Hurry and go.

32
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,950
- Don't tell her I told you to do it.
 - Okay.

33
00:04:55,000 --> 00:04:56,660
Even if...

34
00:04:56,660 --> 00:05:01,090
we haven't known each other for a long time, and I haven't been in Paris for long,

35
00:05:01,090 --> 00:05:04,080
I feel like we're colleagues.

36
00:05:04,080 --> 00:05:07,050
Today is the last time we will see each other.

37
00:05:07,050 --> 00:05:09,840
Tomorrow, I'll be heading back to Shanghai.

38
00:05:11,300 --> 00:05:14,240
Do you have anything you want to say to me?

39
00:05:15,290 --> 00:05:17,170
Translate, please.

40
00:05:17,170 --> 00:05:21,200
Please give this cute woman a hug.

41
00:05:29,330 --> 00:05:31,300
Do you have anything to say to me?

42
00:05:31,300 --> 00:05:33,500
- All right. Okay. All right.
- But...

43
00:05:33,500 --> 00:05:35,760
That's enough.

44
00:05:35,760 --> 00:05:39,540
Miss, can you please pull yourself together?

45
00:05:40,320 --> 00:05:43,860
How can I pull myself together?

46
00:05:43,860 --> 00:05:47,850
I have no one to rely on now.

47
00:05:47,850 --> 00:05:51,950
Who can handle being cheated on twice within two short months?

48
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:53,820
Who can take that?

49
00:05:53,820 --> 00:05:57,010
Miss, can you stop being so dramatic?

50
00:05:57,010 --> 00:05:59,920
To Cheng Yang and Bai Xiaoman, the relationship is only a working relationship.

51
00:05:59,920 --> 00:06:02,920
Didn't he already explain it to you?

52
00:06:02,920 --> 00:06:06,130
Then, why don't I misunderstand others? It's just him.

53
00:06:06,130 --> 00:06:08,130
He's the one with the problem.

54
00:06:08,130 --> 00:06:10,420
I must say something to you then.

55
00:06:10,420 --> 00:06:12,910
Because of you, he has given up his job.

56
00:06:12,910 --> 00:06:14,980
If he didn't really love you,

57
00:06:14,980 --> 00:06:17,600
why would he take the risk and go back to China with you?

58
00:06:17,600 --> 00:06:21,650
Fine. Even if you are right,

59
00:06:21,650 --> 00:06:24,280
but I've already given up.

60
00:06:24,280 --> 00:06:26,810
Given up? You should stop being stubborn.

61
00:06:26,810 --> 00:06:31,020
You look at your phone 100 times a day. Who are you waiting to call you?

62
00:06:31,020 --> 00:06:35,370
Mo Fei, why are you still mocking me?

63
00:06:35,370 --> 00:06:38,500
I'm not mocking you. I'm telling you the truth.

64
00:06:38,500 --> 00:06:40,920
You've been together for so many years.

65
00:06:40,920 --> 00:06:44,520
How can you just break up and end it?

66
00:06:47,460 --> 00:06:51,850
Before, Cheng Yang was my everything,

67
00:06:51,850 --> 00:06:53,640
but that is now in the past.

68
00:06:53,640 --> 00:06:57,550
I want to start over. I want to establish myself.

69
00:06:57,550 --> 00:06:59,420
Let's work hard together.

70
00:07:00,710 --> 00:07:04,080
Why don't you pack some more? I'll go out and buy some things.

71
00:07:04,080 --> 00:07:05,860
Then let's have a drink.

72
00:07:05,860 --> 00:07:07,400
All right.

73
00:07:17,600 --> 00:07:19,520
Mo Fei.

74
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:27,310
Mo Fei, I'm sorry about last time.

75
00:07:27,310 --> 00:07:29,340
I was at fault.

76
00:07:31,840 --> 00:07:34,100
I heard Duoduo is leaving.

77
00:07:34,100 --> 00:07:36,880
Can I treat you both to a meal?

78
00:07:37,840 --> 00:07:40,400
Can you let me finish before you go?

79
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:47,520
This time the Cayman's Haute Couture is batik.

80
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:51,050
It's the design method you have been pursuing.

81
00:07:51,050 --> 00:07:56,390
You and I both know with regards to batik, no companies will dare to try it.

82
00:07:56,390 --> 00:07:59,760
Cayman is taking a big risk in boldly making this decision.

83
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:01,910
If it's not well accepted in the market,

84
00:08:01,910 --> 00:08:05,230
no companies will dare to try it again.

85
00:08:05,230 --> 00:08:07,490
Do you dare to accept this challenge?

86
00:08:10,460 --> 00:08:14,630
The Chinese style on the market now is really out of place.

87
00:08:14,630 --> 00:08:17,460
If you want to do classic Chinese style design,

88
00:08:17,460 --> 00:08:21,840
Cayman's Haute Couture is your opportunity this time.

89
00:08:21,840 --> 00:08:26,170
If you are willing, I want to collaborate with you.

90
00:08:26,170 --> 00:08:31,220
I'm sure we will defeat the Japanese, Americans, and Spanish.

91
00:08:35,370 --> 00:08:37,760
What do you think? Tell me.

92
00:08:59,890 --> 00:09:02,230
- What do you think? It's okay?
- Not bad. It's much better than me.

93
00:09:02,230 --> 00:09:04,340
- Seriously?
- Yes.
- Today, Linda even complimented you.

94
00:09:04,340 --> 00:09:06,940
- It's true.
- Okay, I'll buy you a meal next time.

95
00:09:06,940 --> 00:09:09,330
- Okay. Bye-bye.
- Bye-bye.

96
00:09:16,680 --> 00:09:18,770
Mo Fan.

97
00:09:20,030 --> 00:09:21,560
Thank you.

98
00:09:21,560 --> 00:09:24,530
- W-Will you be singing at the bar today?
- Yes.

99
00:09:24,530 --> 00:09:26,970
Can I come and listen to you sing?

100
00:09:26,970 --> 00:09:30,160
Okay. If someone goes there, the boss will be happy.

101
00:09:30,160 --> 00:09:33,180
The boss being happy has nothing to do with me.

102
00:09:33,180 --> 00:09:35,250
I hope you will be happy.

103
00:09:35,250 --> 00:09:38,620
Mo Fan, can I bring banners there?

104
00:09:40,680 --> 00:09:42,960
I was joking.

105
00:09:42,960 --> 00:09:44,930
Well...

106
00:09:44,930 --> 00:09:47,760
If there is nothing else, I'm heading out first.

107
00:09:47,760 --> 00:09:51,110
- Thank you for the water.
- Don't need to be polite with me.

108
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:58,180
Lu Zhu, how did you know I finished my water? You especially bought one for me.

109
00:09:58,180 --> 00:10:01,330
Who said it was for you? It's for me.

110
00:10:01,330 --> 00:10:03,370
You... Two bottles?

111
00:10:03,370 --> 00:10:06,390
I like to drink water. Why do you care?

112
00:10:15,320 --> 00:10:17,120
Zhu Zhu,

113
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:19,310
what's the matter? Did Linda scold you again?

114
00:10:19,310 --> 00:10:22,070
Yes. I love to get scolded daily. How can I compare to you?

115
00:10:22,070 --> 00:10:24,760
You are Linda's treasure. I'm like the grass on the roadside.

116
00:10:24,760 --> 00:10:26,560
I-I-I said the wrong thing.

117
00:10:26,560 --> 00:10:28,820
You are the treasure and I'm the grass on the roadside, okay?

118
00:10:28,820 --> 00:10:31,500
Zhu Zhu...

119
00:10:31,500 --> 00:10:34,960
Let's forget about training. Kitty is coming to the bar to hear me sing tonight. Why don't you come, too?

120
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:36,880
Me?

121
00:10:36,880 --> 00:10:39,530
Why would I go with her?

122
00:10:41,550 --> 00:10:44,040
Did you have some misunderstanding?

123
00:10:44,040 --> 00:10:46,380
You were very fiece with her last time.

124
00:10:46,380 --> 00:10:49,010
Kitty doesn't seem to have a good attitude lately.

125
00:10:49,010 --> 00:10:52,950
If there is anything, why don't you talk it out? We're all friends.

126
00:10:52,950 --> 00:10:56,910
Who wants to be her friend? You can be her friend. I won't.

127
00:10:56,910 --> 00:10:59,730
Lu Zhu, why can't you be more reasonable?

128
00:10:59,730 --> 00:11:03,510
I don't see how Kitty might have offended you, but you keep aiming at her.

129
00:11:03,510 --> 00:11:07,350
Right. I'm unreasonable. I'm the most unreasonable person, okay?

130
00:11:07,350 --> 00:11:10,640
No... I didn't mean it like that.

131
00:11:10,640 --> 00:11:13,310
Well... How about this? If you come, I'll treat you to dinner.

132
00:11:13,310 --> 00:11:15,680
I'm not going.

133
00:11:42,940 --> 00:11:45,080
I want to share something with all of you.

134
00:11:45,080 --> 00:11:46,850
- Go ahead.
- When I went to Paris this time...

135
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:50,570
Mingxuan, eat first.

136
00:11:51,580 --> 00:11:53,290
Director Xia.

137
00:11:57,490 --> 00:11:59,340
Director Xia.

138
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:00,830
What?

139
00:12:02,240 --> 00:12:04,690
The meeting with President Wu is set for 2:00 p.m. today.

140
00:12:04,690 --> 00:12:09,080
We have to finalize the proposal. President Wu is super anxious.

141
00:12:09,080 --> 00:12:12,260
He sent people to ask us many times. He's afraid something might go wrong,

142
00:12:12,260 --> 00:12:15,390
and our design sketch was already sent to the factory.

143
00:12:15,390 --> 00:12:18,080
If you don't have any more changes, please sign.

144
00:12:18,080 --> 00:12:20,250
- Then we can start production.
- Okay.

145
00:12:20,250 --> 00:12:22,780
And the Milan meeting is also very urgent.

146
00:12:22,780 --> 00:12:25,730
If you have time, please call JK immediately.

147
00:12:25,730 --> 00:12:27,580
I know.

148
00:12:28,240 --> 00:12:29,320
What's the matter?

149
00:12:29,320 --> 00:12:31,080
I'm fine.

150
00:12:31,940 --> 00:12:33,130
[Shut down]

151
00:12:35,130 --> 00:12:37,200
Something on your mind?

152
00:12:42,910 --> 00:12:45,410
Where are you going?

153
00:12:45,410 --> 00:12:49,130
For the meeting later, you can't be late.

154
00:12:49,130 --> 00:12:51,810
You have been tired from work recently, right?

155
00:12:51,810 --> 00:12:53,160
No.

156
00:12:53,160 --> 00:12:56,820
You should take a break. Haven't you always wanted to go to Switzerland?

157
00:12:56,820 --> 00:12:59,150
Switzerland?

158
00:12:59,150 --> 00:13:02,080
All right. Will the company pay for it?

159
00:13:02,080 --> 00:13:06,220
Why did you buy such a late flight? It's not safe.

160
00:13:06,220 --> 00:13:07,620
I had no other choice.

161
00:13:07,620 --> 00:13:10,660
The red-eye tickets are the cheapest.

162
00:13:10,660 --> 00:13:11,990
Let me hug you.

163
00:13:11,990 --> 00:13:15,830
- You're leaving.
- I can't bear to leave you.
- Be safe on the way.

164
00:13:15,830 --> 00:13:19,500
I will miss you. Take care of yourself.

165
00:13:19,500 --> 00:13:22,890
Send me a WeChat when you get to the airport. You can even call.

166
00:13:22,890 --> 00:13:25,320
When I'm in Shanghai, I'll come and visit you.

167
00:13:25,320 --> 00:13:28,700
I'll come over to your house for a meal. You can also come to my house for a meal, too.

168
00:13:28,700 --> 00:13:31,270
I'll take you to see my brother.

169
00:13:32,600 --> 00:13:34,680
Cheng Yang is such a bastard.

170
00:13:34,680 --> 00:13:39,040
I made a WeChat Moments post after I bought the ticket. He didn't even pay attention to me.

171
00:13:39,040 --> 00:13:42,370
Say, I'm leaving and he didn't come and see me off.

172
00:13:42,370 --> 00:13:44,420
He hasn't even given me a call the last few days.

173
00:13:44,420 --> 00:13:48,400
If you want to call him, take the initiative. This is what you taught me.

174
00:13:48,400 --> 00:13:52,230
But our situation is different.

175
00:13:52,230 --> 00:13:53,820
The car is here.

176
00:13:53,820 --> 00:13:56,990
I didn't call this ride.

177
00:13:56,990 --> 00:13:58,710
It's not.

178
00:14:02,730 --> 00:14:05,320
Come on, go.

179
00:14:05,320 --> 00:14:09,350
Duoduo, I saw your WeChat Moments post.

180
00:14:09,350 --> 00:14:12,430
I'm taking the same flight as you. Let's go back home together.

181
00:14:12,430 --> 00:14:14,540
I can't live without you.

182
00:14:14,540 --> 00:14:17,800
You said you can't live without me, so I must be with you?

183
00:14:17,800 --> 00:14:20,660
Besides, did I forgive you?

184
00:14:20,660 --> 00:14:23,570
Wait. Wait. I already called for a car.

185
00:14:23,570 --> 00:14:25,610
Wait, listen. If you don't leave now, you'll be late.

186
00:14:25,610 --> 00:14:27,390
Sir, please help. Thank you.

187
00:14:27,390 --> 00:14:31,060
If it doesn't work, then split the payment with him.

188
00:14:31,060 --> 00:14:35,940
Fine. I'll give you the money when we get in the car. I don't want to owe you anything.

189
00:14:35,940 --> 00:14:38,080
All right. Let's get in first. You can pay me when we get to the airport.

190
00:14:38,080 --> 00:14:39,240
All right. Go.

191
00:14:39,240 --> 00:14:41,000
Wait.

192
00:14:46,580 --> 00:14:49,050
Give me a call when you return to Shanghai.

193
00:14:49,050 --> 00:14:53,050
I'll definitely come and find you. Don't worry.

194
00:14:53,050 --> 00:14:54,200
I'm leaving.

195
00:14:54,200 --> 00:14:58,030
All right. Go, go. Go.

196
00:15:04,180 --> 00:15:07,510
- We're leaving.
- Bye-bye.

197
00:15:16,390 --> 00:15:19,240
I'm sorry, President Wu. Please wait for a bit longer.

198
00:15:26,250 --> 00:15:27,660
President Wu.

199
00:15:27,660 --> 00:15:29,800
President Tang.

200
00:15:29,800 --> 00:15:31,250
Director Xia isn't here, yet?

201
00:15:31,250 --> 00:15:33,210
That's right. We've been waiting for her.

202
00:15:33,210 --> 00:15:35,890
I went to her office to look for her and didn't see her.

203
00:15:35,890 --> 00:15:37,220
Is that so?

204
00:15:37,220 --> 00:15:39,720
She's usually very punctual.

205
00:15:42,940 --> 00:15:43,840
Hello.

206
00:15:43,840 --> 00:15:46,690
Brother Xuan, Director Xia turned off her phone.

207
00:15:46,690 --> 00:15:49,990
I've contacted Liu Pei. Liu Pei doesn't seem to be at the company.

208
00:15:50,980 --> 00:15:52,690
Give me a minute.

209
00:15:55,870 --> 00:15:59,430
It's working hours. Why isn't she at the company?

210
00:15:59,430 --> 00:16:04,060
I heard that she's taking annual leave and Director Xia approved it.

211
00:16:09,570 --> 00:16:10,880
President Tang, I'm Manager Wang.

212
00:16:10,880 --> 00:16:13,890
The factory manager said that Director Xia didn't sign the new order contract.

213
00:16:13,890 --> 00:16:17,030
Fashion Daily is in a rush to have this batch of clothing. I can't get into contact with Director Xia.

214
00:16:17,030 --> 00:16:20,890
This is what we'll do. Wait for me at the factory.

215
00:16:20,890 --> 00:16:23,110
I'll be right there to handle it.

216
00:16:23,110 --> 00:16:24,780
Okay.

217
00:16:26,490 --> 00:16:29,200
I'm sorry, President Wu.

218
00:16:29,200 --> 00:16:31,610
Let's push back our meeting.

219
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,910
No.

220
00:16:34,910 --> 00:16:37,150
Hello, President Tang.

221
00:16:37,150 --> 00:16:41,370
Before Director Xia left, did she leave any instructions?

222
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:44,490
No.

223
00:16:44,490 --> 00:16:49,900
President Tang, this is the information of the designers that Director Xia talked to in Milan. She told me to revise it. Anyway, please take a look today.

224
00:16:49,900 --> 00:16:53,540
President Tang, I have five clothing samples waiting for Director Xia's confirmation.

225
00:16:53,540 --> 00:16:57,950
If she doesn't confirm, we won't be able to proceed with the next step.

226
00:16:57,950 --> 00:17:00,840
From now on, send all of Director Xia's work

227
00:17:00,840 --> 00:17:03,000
to my office.

228
00:17:06,490 --> 00:17:09,390
Yes, I can't contact Director Xia either.

229
00:17:09,390 --> 00:17:11,240
Boss.

230
00:17:11,240 --> 00:17:13,450
President Tang! President Tang!

231
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:17,390
Brother Xuan, Director Xia's calls are all forwarded to my phone.

232
00:17:17,390 --> 00:17:19,590
How should I reply?

233
00:17:20,360 --> 00:17:23,090
From now on, send all of Director Xia's work

234
00:17:23,090 --> 00:17:25,520
to the general manager's office.

235
00:17:25,520 --> 00:17:27,690
What?

236
00:17:27,690 --> 00:17:29,810
Well...

237
00:17:31,810 --> 00:17:33,150
Anything else?

238
00:17:33,150 --> 00:17:35,070
There was a call

239
00:17:35,070 --> 00:17:37,590
from Robert, the designer of JK in Milan.

240
00:17:37,590 --> 00:17:41,560
He said he'd only talk to Director Xia.

241
00:17:42,670 --> 00:17:44,380
I understand.

242
00:17:50,780 --> 00:17:53,280
- Brother Xuan.
- Get out.

243
00:17:59,730 --> 00:18:02,430
Hey, Robert.

244
00:18:04,220 --> 00:18:06,250
It's Mingxuan.

245
00:18:20,680 --> 00:18:22,910
Xueling did come home today.

246
00:18:22,910 --> 00:18:25,800
But when she left, she took some luggage with her.

247
00:18:25,800 --> 00:18:28,820
She said she was going on a business trip.

248
00:18:28,820 --> 00:18:32,240
She... Where would she have gone?

249
00:18:33,720 --> 00:18:35,230
Mingxuan.

250
00:18:35,230 --> 00:18:37,000
Old Xia.

251
00:18:37,000 --> 00:18:38,790
We can't find Xueling.

252
00:18:38,790 --> 00:18:41,800
She has turned off her phone. Should we call the police?

253
00:18:41,800 --> 00:18:44,860
She took luggage with her. Why would you call the police?

254
00:18:44,860 --> 00:18:48,540
