that means many things haven't changed. Does it mean you—

517
00:39:10,290 --> 00:39:13,380
But now, the place hasn't changed but the people have changed.

518
00:39:21,470 --> 00:39:26,400
So President Wu's sales proposal has been confirmed?

519
00:39:26,400 --> 00:39:28,240
Yes.

520
00:39:29,770 --> 00:39:33,000
The new designs are in production, too?

521
00:39:33,000 --> 00:39:34,860
Yes.

522
00:39:38,160 --> 00:39:42,030
