532
00:40:10,140 --> 00:40:12,240
to force me to come and find you.

533
00:40:14,460 --> 00:40:16,640
You should know very well.

534
00:40:17,560 --> 00:40:21,140
I'm the type that separates business and personal matters.

535
00:40:21,870 --> 00:40:24,930
